== 影響 ==
此次地震造成一名卡車司機和一名警察死亡，數十人受傷，500戶損毀<ref name="Tajikistan">{{cite news|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/1006153/at-least-two-dead-in-earthquake-in-tajikistan/|title=At least two dead in earthquake in Tajikistan|date=8 December 2015|work=[[Agence_France-Presse|AFP]]|accessdate=2016-11-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202451/http://tribune.com.pk/story/1006153/at-least-two-dead-in-earthquake-in-tajikistan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該震央距離{{link-en|1911年薩雷茲地震|1911 Sarez earthquake}}的震央約5.0公里，當時於[[巴爾坦格河|巴爾坦格河]]形成了{{link-en|Usoi天然壩|Usoi Dam}}。

